            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex cert="low">arciae</ex></expan> Ulpiae <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Sossiae Calli<lb break="no" n="3"/>gonae stola<lb break="no" n="4"/>tae matronae <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">so</supplied>dalicium iuve<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">nu</supplied>m Herculano<lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">ru</supplied>m patronae
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): AE 1958: Z. 6/7: Herculano/[rum]; AE 1956: Z. 2/3: Calli/gonae; Z. 3/4: stola/[t]ae; Z. 6/7: Herculano/[rum]. Maßangaben jew. ohne die Höhe von crepido (21) und corona (20) sowie deren Breite und Tiefe.</p>
            </div>
